Introduce a new scons Bit for the pnacl shared newlib work.

Use it to guard the build of slightly modified version of libnacl
which drops pthread stubs and tls support from libnacl as those
are not compatible with the ld.so integration.

Instead we provide code to tap into the tls support provided by ld.so.

